content: My car is a 2018 Honda Civic. I don't have the exact mileage, but I do remember getting it serviced on February 10th, where I replaced the air filter for $25. I also filled up the gas tank around that time, which cost $30. Oh, and by the way, I also got a parking ticket on January 5th near my work for $50, but that's not exactly a maintenance cost, I guess.
